cat << EOF
GlossTeX is a tool for the automatic preparation of glossaries, lists
of acronyms and sorted lists in general for use with LaTeX and MakeIndex.
GlossTeX combines the functionality of acronym and nomencl and provides some
new features. Various binaries are available in the bin subdirectory.
EOF
